N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 98.1 - Civil enforcement by the attorney general

State Regulations

This Chapter shall not prohibit the Attorney General from initiating any civil
action or proceeding authorized by law for failure to register and/or file reports pursuant to, and/or comply with, any provision of EPTL article 8
or article 7-A, any other law or the common law. Notes
